        "title": "Force ActionBar to show the complete title without truncation?",
        "body": "<p>I have an ActionBar title like this: <\/p>\n\n<pre><code>String title = \"This is a very looooooooooooong text.\";\nsetTitle(title);\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>My ActionBar truncates the title to be: <\/p>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://i.sstatic.net/H2liL.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/H2liL.png\" alt=\"enter image description here\"><\/a><\/p>\n\n<p><strong>How can I force ActionBar to show the complete title without truncation?<\/strong><\/p>\n",
